    'description' => 'Back up or export a SQLite database to SQL dump format (CREATE TABLE + INSERT statements) or CSV. Reads the database schema from sqlite_master, generates portable SQL that recreates tables with indexes and data. Can export individual tables or the entire database. Pure read-only — never modifies the source database. First database backup/export capability in the ecosystem. Never throws — all errors returned as structured data.',
